Dodge County

County in Minnesota, United States of America, North America

Dodge County is a county in Minnesota, United States. The population in Dodge County was 20,981 in 2022. The median age in Dodge County was 38.4 in 2021. The median income in Dodge County was $42,689 in 2021. The unemployment rate in Dodge County was 1.6% in 2023. The percentage of people with obesity in Dodge County was 35.6% in 2021. The percentage of people who binge drink in Dodge County was 20.6% in 2021. The percentage of people who smoke in Dodge County was 15.5% in 2021.
